/*++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+ Given an axis a of an axial algebra A of Monster type, determine if it is of Jordan type 1/4.            +
+                                                                                                          +
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++*/

IsJordanAxis:=function(a)
	 return HasMonsterFusion(a) and {@x[1]:x in Eigenvalues(AdMat(a)) @} eq {@0,1,1/4 @};
end function;
